''Stargate Atlantis'' is an [[United States|American]]-[[Canadian]] [[military science fiction]] [[television series]] and part of [[MGM]]'s [[Stargate|Stargate franchise]]. The series was created by [[Robert C. Cooper]] and [[Brad Wright]] as a spin-off series to ''[[Stargate SG-1]]''. The series has been aired for five seasons and 100 episodes on the US [[Sci Fi Channel (United States)|Sci Fi Channel]]. ''Stargate Atlantis'' premiered on SCI FI on July 16, 2004; its final episode premiered on January 9, 2009.
